    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "resting in the darkness... i don't know. it's just that i feel so disconnected from everything. like i'm already half-gone. i look at his pictures and i just feel like i belong over there with him, not here in this empty house. it feels like the only way to actually be with him again is to stop fighting.",
